What role does the Internet of Things (IoT) play in automotive HMI?
IoT enables vehicle connectivity and seamless integration with mobile devices, enhancing the overall user experience.

What are the advantages of advanced touchscreen displays in HMI systems?
Advanced touchscreen displays offer better resolution, touch sensitivity, and user-friendly interfaces, improving driver interaction.

